creator: MissPap Limited
descriptionHtml:
Shop the latest fashion trends on the move with the Misspap App. Expect iconic pieces with an affordable price tag from our range of women’s clothing, accessories and more. From collections designed in-house that embody Misspap’s signature sexy silhouette to wardrobe staples, inspired by our favourite muses; we are 24/7 premium fast fashion at its best. With our brand new app, you’ve got the statement styles and latest trends at your fingertips.
With hundreds of new styles landing on the app weekly, whether you’re looking for new dresses, accessories, heels, loungewear or something completely different – we’ve got you covered. Not got time to checkout straight away? Simply add items to your wishlist to shop later on the app.
Download the Misspap app to shop the entire range from the tap of your screen. Features include:

• New Products - 100s of new styles added weekly and the latest trends at your fingertips.

• Early Access – Get notified about early access to the latest collaborations before anyone else.

• Exclusives - Get alerts about App only offers and shop exclusive products.

• VIP Delivery - Get Unlimited UK Next Day Delivery for a year and benefit from early access to sales, Black Friday deals and exclusive offers.

• Fast and secure checkout - Enjoy a super-easy and secure checkout with speed. Now with more ways to pay, including PayPal, Klarna and many more.

• Shop now and pay later with Klarna - Buy now and pay later in three easy payments, interest-free.

• Track your order - Order on the app and track where your parcel is until it gets to you.


• Wishlist - Find and save all your favourite pieces for later by adding your next haul to your wishlist. Share your wishlist with friends and family via WhatsApp, Facebook, Email, Pinterest and more.

• Search & Refine – Browse through 1000s of products, search for exactly what you’re looking for and filter products by category, size, colour or price.

• Delivery & Returns – Choose from next day delivery and standard shipping. Shopping made easy with fuss-free returns from the UK and Ireland.

Shop the latest fashion trends on the move with the Misspap App. Expect iconic pieces with an affordable price tag from our range of women’s clothing, accessories and more. From collections designed in-house that embody Misspap’s signature sexy silhouette to wardrobe staples, inspired by our favourite muses; we are 24/7 premium fast fashion at its best. With our brand new app, you’ve got the statement styles and latest trends at your fingertips.
With hundreds of new styles landing on the app weekly, whether you’re looking for new dresses, accessories, heels, loungewear or something completely different – we’ve got you covered. Not got time to checkout straight away? Simply add items to your wishlist to shop later on the app.
Download the Misspap app to shop the entire range from the tap of your screen. Features include:

• New Products - 100s of new styles added weekly and the latest trends at your fingertips.

• Early Access – Get notified about early access to the latest collaborations before anyone else.

• Exclusives - Get alerts about App only offers and shop exclusive products.

• VIP Delivery - Get Unlimited UK Next Day Delivery for a year and benefit from early access to sales, Black Friday deals and exclusive offers.

• Fast and secure checkout - Enjoy a super-easy and secure checkout with speed. Now with more ways to pay, including PayPal, Klarna and many more.

• Shop now and pay later with Klarna - Buy now and pay later in three easy payments, interest-free.

• Track your order - Order on the app and track where your parcel is until it gets to you.


• Wishlist - Find and save all your favourite pieces for later by adding your next haul to your wishlist. Share your wishlist with friends and family via WhatsApp, Facebook, Email, Pinterest and more.

• Search & Refine – Browse through 1000s of products, search for exactly what you’re looking for and filter products by category, size, colour or price.

• Delivery & Returns – Choose from next day delivery and standard shipping. Shopping made easy with fuss-free returns from the UK and Ireland.
